The AI Mental Wellness Companion is designed to support users in maintaining mental wellness. It uses AI techniques, such as sentiment analysis, to understand a userâ€™s mood based on their input. Depending on the detected mood (positive, negative, or neutral), the app offers appropriate suggestions, including affirmations and relaxation techniques.

Key features:

Mood analysis using natural language processing (e.g., TextBlob).
Personalized responses based on user sentiment.
A simple, user-friendly web interface for daily check-ins.
Mental health support through positive reinforcements and coping strategies.
